  <h2>Breadcrumbs</h2>
  <p><strong>INTRODUCTION</strong></p>
  <p>
    The Kickstart <b>breadcrumb</b> component is designed to display current location of the user in the hierarchy of
    pages or process steps. Separators and other designs are added by css.
  </p>
